				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				1 - The value added to my EQ experience by Everlore far outweighs the $15 subscription fee...  for Tunare's sake, we're talking about 4 cents a day folks...<BR>
<BR>
2 - my main concern is about privacy.  will my email address be sold?  I will not subscribe till this question is answered.<BR>
<BR>
3 - qikkiq, im not so sure that the advertisements are served by Everlore...  the ad content comes from a different server source and would therefore not be consuming Everlore purchased bandwidth...  This is the same way a hyperlink works...  If you click on a link from Everlore to ANOTHER site, Everlore does not pay for that bandwidth.  The ads are just being hyperlinked to behind the scenes, your browser does it automatically.
				</font>
